content:
“If the world economy cannot accommodate the largest two trading nations on earth, the results would spell disaster for everyone. We hope the principles we have developed can steer us toward peaceful economic co-existence and away from trade wars with no winners.” -

content: Happy #PurpleDay Started by our seniors last year, the day is now part of the #88Countdown that showcases our #violetpride

name: NYU Shanghai
content: Photo update on NYU Shanghai's new campus. Four interlinked structures surrounding a courtyard are reminiscent of both a traditional US-style college quad and Chinese scholar’s garden. Construction of the 115,000 square meter campus is on track for completion in summer 2022.
